Class TimeStampLogger

    public class TimeStampLogger
extends java.lang.Object
implements IStatistics
    The TimeStampLogger Loggs SystenTimeStamps of each OFPAcketOut and OFPacketIn -> Can be Used for IAT of two OF_PACKET_INs

    Christopher Metter(christopher.metter@informatik.uni-wuerzburg.de)
